											<span id="DataList1__ctl3_Label1"><font face="Verdana" size="1"><P>The item database has been deployed.&nbsp; You can now search for items to add as a purchase/loot award instead of using your own items that you enter.&nbsp; This will keep item stats consistent, and save you a bunch of work not having to add and maintain your own item list.&nbsp; When you add a purchase, you will see a box to enter your search for the item.&nbsp; After you click the search button, a results grid comes up.. check the item you want, and pick the player and raid, and you are all set.&nbsp; You can also click on the item before you add it to see the stats, to make sure you are adding the right item.</P>
<P>If anyone notices an error or problem with this patch, please email me right away.&nbsp;I usually spend a few hours testing and watching for errors, but I am dead tired :)</P>
<P>I am going to fix some small problems with user-interface, and then start working on the Color Configuration page.&nbsp; I want to have it so when you are picking your colors, you dont have to post back to the server with ever choice.. it gets tedious.</P>
