											<span id="DataList1__ctl9_Label1"><font face="Verdana" size="1"><P>I added full sorting to the raid list.&nbsp; You can now sort by name, date, participants etc.&nbsp; If you click the same column twice, you can sort ascending or descending.&nbsp; I can`t believe I didn`t do this before, it just kept getting forgotten I guess.</P>
<P>There was a bug in my graphics handling engine, which caused Gif images to get converted to jpeg images.&nbsp; It wasn`t a big deal, unless the gif was animated, or had transparent backgrounds.&nbsp; This is now fixed, and my engine will output gifs as gifs.&nbsp; This engine is the one that checks to make sure nobody is hot-linking pictures to the server.&nbsp; </P>
<P>I also increased the timeout timer for logins.&nbsp; So if you are logged in and editing your news or whever, it won`t make you login if you spend more than 30minutes of inactivity (typing etc).&nbsp; It now gives you 60 minutes.</P>
<P>I am probably going to implement an items database in the next patch.&nbsp; This will allow you to pick items from a centralized list with proper stats/graphics and simply assign your value to the item upon purchase.&nbsp; I have to implement it so its backwards compatible with the existing system, hopefully it won`t be&nbsp;a big deal :)</P>
<P>Also, the new raid dump feature of the Guild Manager in EQ will be coded in.. i just need someone to email me a sample of the dump so I can code up my parser to accept it.&nbsp; Ironically, I am not in a guild, and don`t have access to a sample file right now.&nbsp; So if someone can email me with a sample file, that would be great!</P></font></span>
